title: Quick Crumbed Chicken & Lemony Roast Veggie Couscous with Garlic Dip & Slivered Almonds
description: Consider plain chicken breast strips a thing of the past: in this recipe, your chicken gets gussied up in a gorgeous golden breadcrumb
topping with complementary spices. You’ll pan-fry it for a healthier alternative, then lay it on a bed of lemony veggie couscous and
drizzle over garlicky yoghurt. Simple, satisfying, and supercharged with flavor—what more could you ask for?

